{"tid":1521802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警賊，貪生怕死","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:59:34.000Z","uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4f18af77e5535aba917e6ace1242311ea6b090","tid":1521802,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:51:50.000Z","msg":"又多句口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be38a0d726f801b14d466de5b4303ba4ef91455","tid":1521802,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"80c2ac29b0afea21ad37876934d5097f580423fc","tid":1521802,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還我真普選！<br />\n<br />\nBe Water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2e373084f2f9b5b8a92c42bc3510b7812c6b3f88","tid":1521802,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:13.000Z","msg":"支持警察，吞 。。。"},{"pid":"b44253192a20244d00dd362d2aacf9ac499a7b89","tid":1521802,"uid":82291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"唔好咁叫<br />\n一間激起佢地d鬥志就慘了"},{"pid":"86d64fb0bf591a9df5c4184287c3763ac79c7b83","tid":1521802,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b44253192a20244d00dd362d2aacf9ac499a7b89","tid":1521802,"uid":82291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"唔好咁叫<br />\n一間激起佢地d鬥志就慘了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:57:28.000Z","msg":"然後支持警察....吞"},{"pid":"701c91d068d358233f4ac0590d435dcdc5312eff","tid":1521802,"uid":314979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzZMo85.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzZMo85.gif&h=cc9a1d5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be145bf3a86eb48bc72a0e5c740f4ff4c83e02a2","tid":1521802,"uid":311267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:59:37.000Z","msg":"香港賤賊 賣港狗賊 打人仔女 絕不手軟 叫雞中岀 絕不負責"},{"pid":"58f98f65c8e9cef427b0abea9be465138d80e722","tid":1521802,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:01:1